            </a>
            <a href="/master-data" class="flex items-center gap-4 p-3.5 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/10 rounded-2xl transition">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 8h14M5 8a2 2 0 110-4h14a2 2 0 110 4M5 8v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V8m-9 4h4"></path></svg> Master Data
